=== 拍攝 ===
電影正式於2015年11月4日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]開拍<ref>{{cite news|title=Emily Blunt brings her daughter Hazel to work on set of The Girl On The Train for the first time... but the novel's London location is swapped for New York|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3305057/Emily-Blunt-pictured-looking-dowdy-New-York-set-Girl-Train-time.html|accessdate=2015-11-07|work=dailymail.co.uk|date=2015-11-05|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304123104/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3305057/Emily-Blunt-pictured-looking-dowdy-New-York-set-Girl-Train-time.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=On the Set for 11/6/15: Emily Blunt and Luke Evans Start ‘Girl on the Train’, Brad Pitt Wraps ‘Lost City of Z’|url=http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-11615-emily-blunt-and-luke-evans-start-girl-on-the-train-brad-pitt-wraps-lost-city-of-z/|accessdate=2015-11-07|work=ssninsider.com|date=2015-11-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610110610/http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-11615-emily-blunt-and-luke-evans-start-girl-on-the-train-brad-pitt-wraps-lost-city-of-z/|archivedate=2017-06-10}}</ref>。2016年在1月30日宣布[[殺青|殺青]]。

== 發行 ==
[[華特迪士尼工作室電影|華特迪士尼工作室電影]]定於2016年10月7日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=The Girl On The Train’ Sets Arrival Date|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/the-girl-on-the-train-dreamworks-release-date-1201595657/|accessdate=2015-11-05|work=Deadline.com|date=2015-10-27|archive-date=2020-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303000911/https://deadline.com/2015/10/the-girl-on-the-train-dreamworks-release-date-1201595657/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，[[環球影業|環球影業]]取代了華特迪士尼獲得該片的發行權，而上映日則和原來的相同。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據186條評論，新鮮度44%，平均得分5.4／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_girl_on_the_train_2016/ |title=The Girl on the Train (2016) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-10-04 |archive-date=2016-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009024526/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_girl_on_the_train_2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上獲得48分，評價好壞平均參雜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-girl-on-the-train-2016|title=The Girl on the Train reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-10-04|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126035257/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-girl-on-the-train-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，《列車上的女孩》估計於首週末約能獲得3000萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/birth-of-a-nation-opening-early-tracking-1201862168/|title=‘Birth of a Nation’ and ‘Girl on the Train’ Hit Box Office Tracking: How Will They Fare?|author=Dave McNary|work=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]''|date=2016-10-02|accessdate=2016-10-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108104852/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/birth-of-a-nation-opening-early-tracking-1201862168/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首映週末票房為2470萬美元，位居當週票房冠軍<ref name=deadline>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/the-girl-on-the-train-birth-of-a-nation-weekend-box-office-1201832560/ |title=Hurricane Matthew Doesn’t Slow ‘Girl On The Train’, But Overall Ticket Sales Lower Than Jonas; Controversy Conquers ‘Nation’ |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2016-10-11 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108191146/https://deadline.com/2016/10/the-girl-on-the-train-birth-of-a-nation-weekend-box-office-1201832560/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

